# 📁 Directory Structure

## Customer Pages
```
app/
  page.tsx                              # 메인 (인덱스)
  (auth)/
    signup/page.tsx                     # 회원가입
    login/page.tsx                      # 로그인
  (customer)/
    layout.tsx                          # 고객 레이아웃
    products/page.tsx                   # 상품 리스트
    products/[slug]/page.tsx            # 상품 상세 (캘린더 예약)
    checkout/page.tsx                   # 결제
```

## Admin Pages
```
app/
  (admin)/
    layout.tsx
    dashboard/page.tsx
    dashboard/reservations/page.tsx
    dashboard/payments/page.tsx
    dashboard/statistics/page.tsx
    products/page.tsx
    products/new/page.tsx
    products/[productId]/edit/page.tsx
```

## Components
```
components/
  ui/                        # shadcn/ui
  common/                    # ✅ 모든 페이지 공유 (header, footer)
    header.tsx
    footer.tsx
  customer/                  # 고객용
    product-card.tsx
    product-carousel.tsx
    booking-calendar.tsx
    reservation-modal.tsx
    payment-form.tsx
  admin/                     # 어드민용
    product-form.tsx
    reservation-table.tsx
    payment-table.tsx
    stats-card.tsx
  dev/                       # 개발용 (배포 시 제거)
    api-test.tsx
```

## Store / Lib
```
store/
  auth-store.ts              # 인증 상태 (여기서만!)
  product-store.ts
  booking-store.ts
  admin-store.ts

lib/
  utils.ts
  supabase.ts
  mock-data.ts
  api/
    auth.ts
    products.ts
    reservations.ts
    payments.ts
```